<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="Language_selection_dropdown">  Language selection dropdown </h1>
<p></p>

<strong>To be included where a language selection is needed, for instance in the top bar or left bar.</strong>
<p></p>

Note: this dropdown is only shown if localization is enabled.<br />
Test: <span style="color:red; font-weight:bold;">localization is not enabled</span> <br />
<p></p>

Usage:
<pre class="tml">
&#37;INCLUDE{&#34;&#37;SYSTEMWEB&#37;.LanguageSelector&#34;}&#37;
</pre>
<p class='p'>Result:</p>

<p class='p'></p>

<!--  <pre class="tml">
